  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bc7\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Wigneswaran announced that he would support Ranil",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Tamil People's National Alliance will give its support to President Ranil Wickremesinghe in return, the party's president CV Wigneswaran has said.",
        "Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe and Member of Parliament Dalus Alagaperuma are vying for the presidential election.",
        "It is noteworthy that while the Tamil National Alliance has extended its support to Dallas Beauty, the Tamil People's National Alliance has announced that it will extend its support to President Ranil Wickremesinghe in return.",
        "Meanwhile, it is noted that Vikineswaran handed over a letter containing 6 demands on behalf of the Tamil people to the Acting President and new presidential candidate Ranil Wickramasinghe on Tuesday 19th."
      ],
